<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Egloffstein, Amtmann zu Forchheim</head><p>Der Rat bittet wegen Verweigerung des Rechts für Fritz Schrecker, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Schiedsgericht und teilt mit, dass er Fritz Schrecker angewiesen hat, die Habe des Armmanns des Adressaten herauszugeben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_156" id="76v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l17"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l18"><expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan> Amptman cʒu voꝛchem</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l19"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des <expan>Fritʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Schreckers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l20">vnſers Burgers vvegen / daʒ haben wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtand<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd haben durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l21">
<add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~</add> denſelben vnſern Burger beſant / vnd ~ darümb cʒu rede geſatʒt / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l23">der hat vns geantvvürt / das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l22">er voꝛmals beÿ euch dauſʒen ſey geweſen vnd </ab></add> Jm das recht biſʒ her von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l24"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> ſeÿ woꝛden / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l25">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab></add> demſelben vnſerm <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> noch <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l26">tag <expan>beſcheide<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jm von dem ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> rechten hellffen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l28">
<add><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l27">Als wir etc / Das <expan>wol<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> So haben vvir <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſern <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran gevveiſt / das er dem ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l29"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſein habe vngehindert volgen ſol laſʒen / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Circu<ex>m</ex>cıſıo<ex>nem</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l31"><expan>d<ex>o</ex>m<ex>ini</ex></expan> Anno Nono / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_156" id="76v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein,
                            <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, amptman czu Vorchem </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des
                            <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Schreckers, unsers burgers, wegen, daz
                        haben wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stand<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben durch
                                    <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> denselben unsern burger besant und
                        darümb czu rede gesaczt und der hat uns geantwürt, das <add>er vormals bey
                            euch dauszen sey gewesen und</add> im das recht bisz her von
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> sey worden.
                            <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir <add>durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen</add> demselben unserm
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> noch <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        tag <expan>bescheide<ex>n</ex></expan> und im von dem
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> rechten hellffen wöllet, <add>als wir
                            etc. Das <expan>wol<ex>en</ex></expan></add>. So haben wir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> unsern
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran geweist, das er dem
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sein habe ungehindert volgen sol
                        laszen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>circu<ex>m</ex>cisio<ex>nem</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>o</ex>m<ex>ini</ex></expan> anno nono.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
